}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#ed826e8e1376ce5d70194c585b183aa2>.
<#ed826e8e1376ce5d70194c585b183aa2> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/2b84284b-4e01-48ee-8f40-5792c42579f2>;
