<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#bef4cce2a1459d4dee0e93af3b23d04d>.
<#bef4cce2a1459d4dee0e93af3b23d04d> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/75076d38-25e6-4ad6-9cb9-878708728f93>;
