_:b0__89521 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((10.00 70.00,25.00 70.00,25.00 55.00,10.00 55.00,10.00 70.00))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
