}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#6c2c0e2dd4bb48b390e3f3f08b52f7bc>.
<#6c2c0e2dd4bb48b390e3f3f08b52f7bc> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
