<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#dfb557f92c59a271a0a2a73498bf7b6c>.
<#dfb557f92c59a271a0a2a73498bf7b6c> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/f28575c2-9229-4445-9324-a41430213fb0>;
