<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/9e3c0b20-cdb2-11eb-9269-d991226864d8> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> _:b0__10050.
_:b0__10050 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((10.00 70.00,25.00 70.00,25.00 55.00,10.00 55.00,10.00 70.00))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
