<#bb08ab3db6d017ee94793d02526a36fe> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/2d236bdc-9ba7-4296-bb96-bb5a2665bfff>;
