<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#91da2ee62ee76861febb7144b38a4c42>.
<#91da2ee62ee76861febb7144b38a4c42> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U25203>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-08T06:32:55.248Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
