<#ab36627e4058b0bb8d38eed4268c4e41> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/ceb61548-b3ad-44b8-94a9-a4526c4eaa4e/resource/d8493646-cbfc-4fad-9c33-0d36435ce156>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-08T06:32:56.960Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#ab36627e4058b0bb8d38eed4268c4e41> {
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/ceb61548-b3ad-44b8-94a9-a4526c4eaa4e/resource/d8493646-cbfc-4fad-9c33-0d36435ce156> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0>;
